column2: He kept saying, 'I quite expected to have seen Mr. Thornton.
column3: He kept saying, 'I quite expected to have seen mr Thornton.

column2: I'm a poor black feckless sheep--childer may clem for aught I can do, unless, parson, yo'd help me?'
column3: I'm a poor black feckless sheep-childer may clem for aught I can do, unless, parson, yo'd help me?'
